Jane Rose https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jane_Rose 0 Jane Rose (February 7, 1913 – June 29, 1979) was an American character actress, perhaps best remembered today as Audrey Dexter, the gently befuddled mother-in-law of Phyllis Lindstrom on the CBS sitcom Phyllis (1975–77).
